.signup
  %h1
    Apply
  .background_check
    = form_for(current_applicant, url: next_step_applicants_path, method: :post) do |f|
      .form-group
        .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          %p.background_check
            I hereby authorize Instacart to investigate my background and qualifications for purposes of evaluating whether
            I am qualified for the position for which I am applying. I understand that Instacart will utilize an outside firm or
            firms to assist it in checking such information, and I specifically authorize such an investigation by
            information services and outside entities of the company's choice.

          %p.background_check
            I also understand that I may withhold my permission and that in such a case,
            no investigation will be done, and my application for employment will not be processed further.

          %p.background_check
            I agree with all the above terms
      .form-group
        .col-md-offset-4.col-md-4
          = f.hidden_field :background_check_consent, value: true
          = f.submit "Submit", class: 'cta'

